00:00:29.330 --> 00:00:33.080
In this session, we'll see how we
can cure our puppy's loneliness

00:00:33.080 --> 00:00:35.400
by storing a collection of other dogs,

00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:39.070
together in the same variable,
using what's known as an array.

00:00:40.240 --> 00:00:42.310
See?
