00:00:51.226 --> 00:00:53.910
We can add in an age for each dog.

00:00:55.040 --> 00:00:56.130
Let's also give them a breed.

00:00:57.170 --> 00:00:59.240
We now have a collection of dogs,

00:00:59.240 --> 00:01:03.560
where each dog consists of
multiple pieces of information.

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:06.740
